{"tid":333423,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"搞乜鬼 DC套正義聯盟拍到成套Marvel爆谷片咁","createTime":"2017-07-23T19:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T14:21:40.000Z","uid":119223,"like":19,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1048bf21b0c74e9179bef4acdcd1cc30cecaf524","tid":333423,"uid":119223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T19:26:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=7vVrPl1CygE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7vVrPl1CygE&d=ojNS2Ttr%2FPNUVTMwEFwojKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=02470de1\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=7vVrPl1CygE</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完條Trailer<br />\n完全感受唔到DC以往帶比人既文藝氣氛<br />\n個種深度沉穩、象徵隱喻、超凡意境<br />\n<br />\n就好似話比你聽超人係耶穌<br />\n佢救世佢受難佢重生<br />\n令世間上既平民百姓都意識到呢種高尚情操<br />\n<br />\nDC電影一直用黑暗角度透露凡間苦惱<br />\n用哲學製作電影，用電影普渡眾生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但見到今次正義聯盟&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n居然充斥各種低俗爛gag橋段 純娛樂動作爆破<br />\n<br />\n我真係好失望&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n要睇無腦爆谷片我不如睇隔離哎呀man xx"},{"pid":"0edf47a259d01301b8cbf3f43ea4f5405b447ba3","tid":333423,"uid":119223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T03:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f5ba5437478bb35336c15379ee5f7f926cf544","tid":333423,"uid":105715,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T04:08:37.000Z","msg":"就算你班on9 DC fans 點吹奏三部曲黑暗都好<br />\n唔收得就係唔收得，你估DC開善堂呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739418508fc9061668d9727dc381bd10ea94854c","tid":333423,"uid":105605,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T04:11:22.000Z","msg":"冇計，主流唔buy咁咪比番屎觀眾食，DL啱晒大部分人口味，但都保留左DC既原素"},{"pid":"7fb8d537916d51cb0a4ac8a934d4ff487ee5d081","tid":333423,"uid":105605,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":